1
00:01:36,772 --> 00:01:40,200
[Episode 15]

2
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,399
About Zhi Hua threatening you...

3
00:01:42,399 --> 00:01:43,800
We all know about it.

4
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:46,159
There is no antidote for Yemotian Poison.

5
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:49,280
Don't let Zhi Hua control you.

6
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,200
Hand him over.

7
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,959
Zhi Hua has no antidote at all.

8
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:54,439
Why do you still refuse to see reason?

9
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:57,632
I'm killing that damn official
not just for the antidote.

10
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,559
Hand over that damn official!

11
00:02:00,559 --> 00:02:03,772
You have a personal grudge
against the Magistrate of Yicheng?

12
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:12,079
If you don't reveal his whereabouts,
don't even think about leaving today!

13
00:02:12,079 --> 00:02:13,879
Bai Yu Tang, have you lost your mind?

14
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,159
Do you realize...

15
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:17,799
the cost of killing a court official?

16
00:02:17,799 --> 00:02:19,560
People handle their own affairs.

17
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:22,799
Repay kindness, avenge wrongs.
I can accept any consequence!

18
00:02:22,799 --> 00:02:25,799
Being so hesitant and fearful,
how can you call yourself a hero?

19
00:02:25,799 --> 00:02:27,640
As for you, Lord Zhan,

20
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,479
the title of Imperial Cat has tamed you
just like that,

21
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:32,320
- stripping you of your martial spirit.
- That's too far!

22
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,199
Don't you know what kind of man Zhan is?

23
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:36,322
- For your sake, he--
- Miss Huo.

24
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,758
There's no need to say more.

25
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,247
If we must bare our hearts for him...

26
00:02:46,247 --> 00:02:49,186
to see the truth and tell friend from foe,

27
00:02:49,186 --> 00:02:51,159
then a friend like this...

28
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:53,995
I can do without!

29
00:02:54,679 --> 00:02:56,120
Miss Huo.

30
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:59,000
You don't need to intervene today.

31
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,780
Let me settle this with him.

32
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:04,799
Now is not the time to be impulsive.

33
00:03:04,799 --> 00:03:06,200
Zhi Hua's men will be here any second.

34
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:08,660
Perfect timing.

35
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:12,672
They can serve as witnesses to our battle.

36
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:20,680
Are you two finished fighting?

37
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,400
- No.
- No!

38
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,400
Then keep fighting until a winner is decided.

39
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,760
Let's go! To the back hill!

40
00:06:08,239 --> 00:06:09,679
Bai Yu Tang.

41
00:06:09,679 --> 00:06:11,840
I always thought you were smart.

42
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,999
I didn't expect you to be this foolish.

43
00:06:13,999 --> 00:06:16,720
You're falling right into Zhi Hua's trap
without even realizing it.

44
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:19,159
Zhi Hua is clearly sowing dissension.

45
00:06:19,159 --> 00:06:20,799
He wants us to fight each other first.

46
00:06:20,799 --> 00:06:22,280
Then he can use you to do his dirty work,

47
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:24,320
and use you to get rid of
the Magistrate of Yicheng.

48
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,760
Can't you see that?

49
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,640
Of course I know what he's up to!

50
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,919
But I don't care!

51
00:06:28,919 --> 00:06:30,559
As for using me,

52
00:06:30,559 --> 00:06:32,760
as long as it's an evil man being killed,
what does it matter?

53
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,712
Let me ask you!

54
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,880
No matter how skilled you are,

55
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,640
can you slay all the evil in the world?

56
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,119
If you kill the Magistrate of Yicheng,

57
00:06:40,119 --> 00:06:41,840
will Yu Lian and the others be saved?

58
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:44,599
Don't make it sound like
you're the only one who can save them!

59
00:06:44,599 --> 00:06:47,239
Once I kill that damn official and Zhi Hua,

60
00:06:47,239 --> 00:06:50,239
I will surely rescue Yu Lian!

61
00:06:50,239 --> 00:06:52,880
If you charge in alone, who can you save?

62
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:55,679
Why should Yu Lian and the others
risk their lives with you?

63
00:06:55,679 --> 00:06:58,522
Enough of your talk!

64
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,559
Bai Yu Tang.

65
00:07:39,559 --> 00:07:41,760
You always say I'm trapped
by the title of Imperial Cat.

66
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,720
But who is the one

67
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,119
who truly cares about that title?

68
00:07:45,119 --> 00:07:47,159
Who was it that caused a ruckus...

69
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,679
in the Bianjing city because of it?

70
00:07:48,679 --> 00:07:50,200
You?

71
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:53,280
You're not worthy of mentioning the Five Rats!

72
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,372
The Five Rats?

73
00:07:55,372 --> 00:07:56,999
You Five Rats...

74
00:07:56,999 --> 00:07:59,897
deserve to be kept in your place by me.

75
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:14,535
The Yemotian Poison has kicked in?

76
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:31,880
The cat-rat battle was truly spectacular.

77
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:35,280
It's a shame the Southern Knight
can no longer fight.

78
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,997
Bai Yu Tang.

79
00:08:36,997 --> 00:08:39,960
Let me finish this for you.

80
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:57,572
I wanted to avenge you.

81
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,359
But there are more important things to do
right now.

82
00:09:01,359 --> 00:09:02,840
Excuses.

83
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,785
They're all excuses.

84
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:08,747
You never intended to avenge me.

85
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,872
Bai Yu Tang!

86
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:30,799
If you really want to avenge me,

87
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:33,210
kill him now!

88
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,759
Bai Yu Tang.

89
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,810
Wake up.

90
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,006
[Yanling]

91
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,730
Bai Yu Tang!

92
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,310
Zhan!

93
00:10:56,119 --> 00:10:58,172
Let's go!

94
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:42,840
Master.

95
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,479
Zhan Zhao was heavily wounded
and fell off the cliff.

96
00:11:44,479 --> 00:11:46,080
His chances of survival are slim.

97
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,200
Bai Yu Tang has also been
controlled by Yemotian Poison.

98
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:50,040
You can focus on organizing
your birthday banquet now.

99
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,440
Is this true?

100
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,560
Absolutely.

101
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,639
Zhan Zhao was killed by Bai Yu Tang.

102
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:57,088
I witnessed it with my own eyes.

103
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,040
Where is the body?

104
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,639
Since you say Zhan Zhao is dead,

105
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:03,479
why didn't you bring back the body?

106
00:12:03,479 --> 00:12:06,080
The terrain where Zhan Zhao fell
is very treacherous.

107
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,239
Searching for him will be quite difficult.

108
00:12:08,239 --> 00:12:09,720
The death soldiers are badly injured.

109
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:12,822
They need to rest before
they can take action again.

110
00:12:14,599 --> 00:12:17,560
Father. Since Zhi Hua is making excuses,

111
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:20,963
let me lead some men
to search for Zhan Zhao's body.

112
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,535
Very well.

113
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,239
You've done a great service this time.

114
00:12:27,239 --> 00:12:29,235
Go and get some rest first.

115
00:12:29,999 --> 00:12:31,399
My injuries are nothing.

116
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:33,359
Now that Zhan Zhao is eliminated,

117
00:12:33,359 --> 00:12:36,110
you can proceed with your plans.

118
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,010
Congratulations, Father.

119
00:12:42,010 --> 00:12:44,479
Once we close the net at the banquet,

120
00:12:44,479 --> 00:12:47,097
you will rule the world.

121
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,452
We still cannot relax.

122
00:12:50,452 --> 00:12:53,599
Even though Zhan Zhao is no longer in the way,

123
00:12:53,599 --> 00:12:56,879
we must still act with caution.

124
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:58,922
I understand.

125
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:22,197
Any news?

126
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,880
But something seems fishy.

127
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,279
With Zhi Hua's skills alone,

128
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:29,840
how could he possibly kill Zhan Zhao?

129
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,559
Was the body seen?

130
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:34,456
No.

131
00:13:37,159 --> 00:13:39,720
He Bo is headstrong.

132
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:42,679
No matter how many times he loses to Zhan Zhao,

133
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:45,600
he never learns his lesson.

134
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,000
Indeed.

135
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,360
Without seeing Zhan Zhao's body,

136
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,600
how can we rest easy?

137
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,519
Let's wait and see for now.

138
00:13:53,519 --> 00:13:55,760
The birthday banquet is approaching.

139
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:58,210
Keep a close eye on things.

140
00:13:58,210 --> 00:14:01,840
This isn't just about He Bo.

141
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:05,410
It concerns His Lordship's great cause.

142
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:23,639
<i>Don't make it sound like
you're the only one who can save them!</i>

143
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:26,279
<i>Once I kill that damn official
and Zhi Hua,</i>

144
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:29,279
<i>I will surely rescue Yu Lian!</i>

145
00:15:29,279 --> 00:15:31,919
<i>If you charge in alone,
who can you save?</i>

146
00:15:31,919 --> 00:15:34,679
<i>Why should Yu Lian and the others
risk their lives with you?</i>

147
00:15:34,679 --> 00:15:37,535
<i>Enough of your talk!</i>

148
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,279
<i>I have a plan.</i>

149
00:15:51,279 --> 00:15:52,679
<i>I promise</i>

150
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:54,399
<i>I will save everyone safely.</i>

151
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:56,040
<i>But I need your participation</i>

152
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,919
<i>to ensure nothing goes wrong.</i>

153
00:15:57,919 --> 00:15:59,240
<i>Once it's done,</i>

154
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,760
<i>I'll take you
to the Magistrate of Yicheng.</i>

155
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:04,272
<i>Can you trust me just this once?</i>

156
00:16:13,159 --> 00:16:15,360
<i>What do you want me to do?</i>

157
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:18,120
<i>Since Zhi Hua wants to see
this Cat-Rat fight so badly,</i>

158
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:20,122
<i>so he can reap the benefits,</i>

159
00:16:20,122 --> 00:16:23,885
<i>why don't we just go with the flow?</i>

160
00:16:34,399 --> 00:16:35,800
When we were acting,

161
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:38,629
was your poisoning real or an act?

162
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:41,439
Of course it was an act.

163
00:16:41,439 --> 00:16:44,060
Didn't you ask me to play along with your act?

164
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:50,679
Shut up.

165
00:16:50,679 --> 00:16:52,910
Is it your turn to ask questions?

166
00:16:54,519 --> 00:16:58,160
Why didn't you tell us
you were poisoned by Yemotian Poison?

167
00:17:02,039 --> 00:17:05,080
Weren't you the one
who said you wanted to part ways with me,

168
00:17:05,080 --> 00:17:08,159
- and stay out of each other's business?
- Stop making excuses.

169
00:17:08,159 --> 00:17:10,325
You must have been poisoned when you
first scouted Zhongxiao Pavilion.

170
00:17:10,325 --> 00:17:12,760
- We hadn't parted ways then.
- That's enough.

171
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:15,279
Is Zhan really all right?

172
00:17:15,279 --> 00:17:16,640
The sword wound is no longer an issue.

173
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,039
But the residual poison is still there.

174
00:17:19,039 --> 00:17:23,120
That day, when I heard Zhi Hua
had poisoned him, I checked his pulse.

175
00:17:23,120 --> 00:17:25,800
His pulse was normal then,
no signs of poisoning.

176
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,573
The poison currently in his body has entered

177
00:17:27,573 --> 00:17:30,559
his meridians but not
his internal organs.

178
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:31,880
That's strange.

179
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,679
When my two sworn brothers were poisoned,

180
00:17:33,679 --> 00:17:35,332
in less than the time it takes
to drink a cup of tea,

181
00:17:35,332 --> 00:17:37,702
the poison reached their hearts.

182
00:17:39,410 --> 00:17:43,910
Hey, do you have some special constitution
that can suppress Yemotian Poison?

183
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:46,710
Take a guess.

184
00:17:55,799 --> 00:17:57,639
In another four hours,

185
00:17:57,639 --> 00:17:59,679
I can purge the remaining poison.

186
00:17:59,679 --> 00:18:01,400
Don't worry.

187
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,159
Then explain this.

188
00:18:03,159 --> 00:18:05,680
Why did you hide the fact
that you were poisoned?

189
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:07,680
Explain yourself.

190
00:18:09,559 --> 00:18:12,279
Hiding it was my fault.

191
00:18:12,279 --> 00:18:14,039
But even though I'm at fault,

192
00:18:14,039 --> 00:18:15,760
Bai Yu Tang is even more at fault.

193
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,567
Right?

194
00:18:18,399 --> 00:18:20,039
- You really are--
- You what?

195
00:18:20,039 --> 00:18:25,172
Do you know how hard Zhan has tried to find
an antidote for your brothers these days?

196
00:18:26,319 --> 00:18:29,372
The Young Master of the Tang Sect has
agreed to prepare the antidote for you.

197
00:18:29,372 --> 00:18:31,559
Just wait two more days.

198
00:18:32,559 --> 00:18:34,335
Thank you.

199
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:36,799
That's it?

200
00:18:36,799 --> 00:18:38,639
People handle their own affairs.

201
00:18:38,639 --> 00:18:40,760
Repay kindness, avenge wrongs.

202
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:44,422
Is this how you people show gratitude?

203
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,372
Thank you so much.

204
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:58,510
Thank you very much.

205
00:19:00,799 --> 00:19:04,359
Your little play was quite a performance.

206
00:19:04,359 --> 00:19:06,359
I couldn't tell
if you were trying to fool Zhi Hua,

207
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:08,147
or trying to mess with me.

208
00:19:08,147 --> 00:19:10,967
- We thought you heard everything.
- I did hear it.

209
00:19:10,967 --> 00:19:14,823
I heard exactly how you planned
to use your own lives as bait.

210
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:18,720
I only regret that I couldn't scold you both
right there.

211
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,839
Since you knew it was a plan,

212
00:19:19,839 --> 00:19:21,443
- then why did you--
- The injury was real.

213
00:19:21,443 --> 00:19:22,799
Falling off the cliff was also real.

214
00:19:22,799 --> 00:19:25,160
This plan was far too dangerous.

215
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,799
If the sword had been off by an inch,

216
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:29,079
or if the Heavenward Crane Strike
hadn't protected you,

217
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:31,790
wouldn't you really be dead?

218
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:38,239
She's saying she was worried about you.

219
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:12,720
How did you find this place last night?

220
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:15,920
This wasn't part of the plan.

221
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,799
Didn't you both know I was coming all alone?

222
00:20:17,799 --> 00:20:20,440
Because I knew you'd be
worried about Zhan's safety,

223
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:22,160
so I specifically left plums for you.

224
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,519
I wasn't worried about him.

225
00:20:23,519 --> 00:20:25,079
The Moon Envoy was the worried one.

226
00:20:25,079 --> 00:20:27,839
She came to the secret room and
learned about the fake death plan.

227
00:20:27,839 --> 00:20:30,200
She feared he'd mess up the act
and end up as a dead cat for real.

228
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:33,572
So she let me out while Zhi Hua
was regulating his breathing.

229
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:40,210
The Moon Envoy would never
call Zhan a dead cat.

230
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,839
After being away for these days,

231
00:20:51,839 --> 00:20:54,754
don't you have anything to say to us?

232
00:20:58,984 --> 00:21:00,497
I was reckless before. I'm sorry--

233
00:21:00,497 --> 00:21:02,120
- That's not it.
- Then what is it?

234
00:21:02,120 --> 00:21:03,519
I want to know...

235
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:06,510
how you've been these past few days.

236
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:15,519
You're worried that your two sworn brothers...

237
00:21:15,519 --> 00:21:17,920
will be forced by Zhi Hua.

238
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,039
And you've done things against your will.

239
00:21:20,039 --> 00:21:22,622
You must be suffering inside.

240
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:28,440
But you're lucky you met the two of us.

241
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:30,246
With us by your side from now on,

242
00:21:30,246 --> 00:21:32,997
you won't have to suffer anymore.

243
00:21:34,247 --> 00:21:36,640
Why are you telling me this?

244
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,600
You're making me feel guilty.

245
00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:41,085
That's exactly what I intended.

246
00:21:45,759 --> 00:21:47,680
Oh, right.

247
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,239
You said before...

248
00:21:49,239 --> 00:21:51,479
that you didn't kill the Magistrate
for the antidote.

249
00:21:51,479 --> 00:21:53,345
Then for what?

250
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:56,319
What else?

251
00:21:56,319 --> 00:22:00,400
I simply wanted to kill every one
of those villains in Xiangzhou.

252
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,079
If you had killed the Magistrate,

253
00:22:02,079 --> 00:22:05,479
the stigma Zhan carries
would be very hard to clear.

254
00:22:05,479 --> 00:22:07,799
And you would become a wanted criminal.

255
00:22:07,799 --> 00:22:10,695
You knew the consequences.

256
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:15,479
Zhan Zhao should have been
a hero roaming the world.

257
00:22:15,479 --> 00:22:17,239
So what if he carries the stigma?

258
00:22:17,239 --> 00:22:19,319
So what if he's a wanted criminal?

259
00:22:19,319 --> 00:22:23,440
If they still won't let him go,
I'll kill everyone who comes after him.

260
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,279
As for me...

261
00:22:25,279 --> 00:22:29,880
the court can't use a piece of paper
to define whether I'm a hero or a bandit.

262
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:33,799
They didn't give me justice 15 years ago.

263
00:22:33,799 --> 00:22:37,734
Now, I'll take it back with my own hands.

264
00:22:38,519 --> 00:22:40,680
15 years ago?

265
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:42,800
What happened then?

266
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,999
Why isn't Zhan Zhao out yet?

267
00:22:46,999 --> 00:22:49,135
I'll go check on him.

268
00:22:59,519 --> 00:23:01,720
So he was already fine when you came out.

269
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:03,039
And you didn't even tell me.

270
00:23:03,039 --> 00:23:05,347
You didn't ask.

271
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:07,799
Fine.

272
00:23:07,799 --> 00:23:09,440
It's about time.

273
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:11,280
I should go back and play my part as a puppet.

274
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:13,840
When do we strike, Lord Zhan?

275
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:18,319
Finish what you were saying first.

276
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:21,060
Then we'll tell you the rest of the plan.

277
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:24,200
We just didn't want you to be bored,

278
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:26,400
so we wanted you to speak your mind.

279
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,920
Since you're not willing to talk...

280
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,039
then so be it.

281
00:23:29,039 --> 00:23:31,599
As for the rest of the plan, that depends on...

282
00:23:31,599 --> 00:23:35,197
how the Jing family's birthday banquet
preparation goes.

283
00:23:56,039 --> 00:23:58,160
My Lord, you've been in a good mood lately.

284
00:23:58,160 --> 00:24:00,920
I've specially had some wine warmed up.

285
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:04,232
Have a good rest this afternoon.

286
00:24:04,879 --> 00:24:08,039
You've really changed your tune today.

287
00:24:08,039 --> 00:24:11,599
It's rare to hear you speak to me so kindly.

288
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:14,799
Well, your birthday banquet is coming up soon.

289
00:24:14,799 --> 00:24:16,559
I'm happy for you too.

290
00:24:16,559 --> 00:24:19,079
I'll warm up some hangover soup for you.

291
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:21,540
You can drink it when you wake up.

292
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,880
The mountain path is steep and muddy.

293
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,799
Don't be impatient and take shortcuts.

294
00:24:47,799 --> 00:24:50,599
Taking the main road will do.

295
00:24:50,599 --> 00:24:51,920
Once the operation begins,

296
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:54,400
He Bo will focus on you.

297
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,847
You must protect yourself.

298
00:24:58,147 --> 00:25:00,747
Only then can we be at ease.

299
00:25:00,747 --> 00:25:02,359
Don't worry.

300
00:25:02,359 --> 00:25:03,839
You always agree so quickly,

301
00:25:03,839 --> 00:25:06,372
but following through is a different story.

302
00:25:10,279 --> 00:25:13,322
Alright, I'm leaving. Wait for me.

303
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:38,240
Keep this for me for now.

304
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,485
Give it back to me when I return.

305
00:25:42,519 --> 00:25:46,960
You must never risk your life like that.

306
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,585
Alright.

307
00:25:49,585 --> 00:25:51,210
I'm off.

308
00:26:27,039 --> 00:26:28,400
Commander Shao.

309
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,885
Have you found Ling Long?

310
00:26:29,885 --> 00:26:30,920
Not yet.

311
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:33,879
The rain was too heavy last night,
washing away all the footprints.

312
00:26:33,879 --> 00:26:36,991
It's very difficult to find Miss Huo's trail.

313
00:26:37,559 --> 00:26:39,647
What about the Jing Mansion?

314
00:26:39,647 --> 00:26:41,039
Nothing unusual.

315
00:26:41,039 --> 00:26:42,920
They are preparing for the birthday banquet.

316
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,920
They also sent men to look for Zhan Zhao.

317
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:46,920
Zhi Hua hasn't made a move.

318
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:49,445
He should still be in Zhongxiao Pavilion.

319
00:26:50,079 --> 00:26:52,072
Keep watching then.

320
00:26:52,072 --> 00:26:57,660
[The Jing Mansion]

321
00:27:14,839 --> 00:27:16,885
Stop! Stop! Stop!

322
00:27:21,400 --> 00:27:22,640
Who are you people?

323
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:26,541
My Lord.
They are here to tailor new clothes for Madam.

324
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:48,510
I asked them to come.

325
00:27:59,599 --> 00:28:00,800
It's almost dark.

326
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:03,599
Why are you inviting tailors now, Mother?

327
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:05,160
Lord Jing's birthday is coming up.

328
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:08,559
If I don't start now,
I won't be ready in time to wear.

329
00:28:08,559 --> 00:28:11,879
If you have time, come with me to be measured.

330
00:28:11,879 --> 00:28:14,672
I'll have a few new outfits made for you too.

331
00:28:14,672 --> 00:28:17,760
Thank you, Mother, but that's necessary.

332
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:20,460
Then I'll take them inside first.

333
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,160
You.

334
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:27,839
Bring this chest to my room later.

335
00:28:27,839 --> 00:28:29,247
Yes, sir.

336
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:44,960
Take them to the storeroom
to pick out the fabrics first.

337
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:47,880
The rest of you, follow me to be measured.

338
00:28:57,079 --> 00:28:59,799
Thank you for your help, Mrs. Jing.

339
00:28:59,799 --> 00:29:01,760
At noon, I took advantage
of Jing Yi Ming's good mood,

340
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:03,285
and urged him to have a few more drinks.

341
00:29:03,285 --> 00:29:05,521
He should be asleep by now. We must hurry.

342
00:29:05,521 --> 00:29:07,039
Thank you, Mrs. Jing.

343
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:08,722
Let's go.

344
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,960
I'm here to get you out.

345
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,319
I know you.

346
00:29:34,319 --> 00:29:37,360
You're the one who fought He Bo
in the secret room last time.

347
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:40,079
Follow me closely. I'll get you out of here.

348
00:29:40,079 --> 00:29:43,360
No matter what happens, do not be afraid.

349
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:50,035
Put this on.

350
00:29:54,079 --> 00:29:56,440
What do you think of my skills?

351
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,160
Your skills are excellent.

352
00:29:58,160 --> 00:30:00,119
Even He Bo is a bit afraid of you.

353
00:30:00,119 --> 00:30:01,400
In that case,

354
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,000
set your mind at ease.

355
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,122
I will definitely get you out.

356
00:30:07,079 --> 00:30:08,597
Okay.

357
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:17,799
Yu Lian, go.

358
00:30:17,799 --> 00:30:19,359
Once you leave this manor,

359
00:30:19,359 --> 00:30:21,400
you'll never have to fear Jing Yi Ming anymore.

360
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:24,935
Madam, please come with me.

361
00:30:25,799 --> 00:30:27,599
I still have unfinished business.

362
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:29,319
- Mrs. Jing...
- Don't worry.

363
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:32,279
I have my own ways to deal with Jing Yi Ming.

364
00:30:32,279 --> 00:30:35,400
Once you make his crimes public,

365
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:38,160
I can leave with the girls
from Zhongxiao Pavilion...

366
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,960
with dignity...

367
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:42,485
and leave this place openly.

368
00:30:42,485 --> 00:30:43,760
Yu Lian.

369
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:46,119
When the dust settles,

370
00:30:46,119 --> 00:30:49,000
you must forget everything here.

371
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:52,779
And pursue your own carefree life.

372
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,000
Don't cry.

373
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:56,079
Go now.

374
00:30:56,079 --> 00:30:57,600
You can't delay any longer.

375
00:30:57,600 --> 00:30:59,440
Go, go, go.

376
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,760
Go!

377
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,079
Mrs. Jing,

378
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:04,135
please take care.

379
00:31:30,799 --> 00:31:32,597
Master.

380
00:31:35,279 --> 00:31:36,779
Father.

381
00:31:37,359 --> 00:31:39,797
Get out! All of you, get out!

382
00:31:44,079 --> 00:31:46,680
Father. Shao Ji Zu's men sent word.

383
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:48,355
They said Zhan Zhao's body was never found.

384
00:31:48,355 --> 00:31:49,360
I haven't found it either.

385
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:50,759
This is likely a trick.

386
00:31:50,759 --> 00:31:53,079
I knew Zhi Hua wasn't that capable.

387
00:31:53,079 --> 00:31:54,320
We were indeed fooled!

388
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:56,520
Is this the time to gloat?

389
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:57,920
Order the manor to be sealed now!

390
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:59,600
Yes, sir.

391
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,200
Why are you following me?

392
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,680
Go inform Zhi Hua immediately!

393
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,640
Bai Yu Tang must have been faking it.

394
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,445
Yes, sir.

395
00:32:10,039 --> 00:32:11,479
They caught us.

396
00:32:11,479 --> 00:32:13,480
We've been spotted.

397
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:15,185
Yu Lian,

398
00:32:15,185 --> 00:32:18,060
did you forget what Mrs. Jing just said?

399
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:45,207
Looking for me?

400
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:51,631
You weren't poisoned?

401
00:32:52,279 --> 00:32:56,672
Keeping my neck stiff like that
was exhausting for me.

402
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,785
Looking for this?

403
00:33:04,559 --> 00:33:06,827
Kill Zhi Hua!

404
00:33:39,519 --> 00:33:41,235
Wait.

405
00:33:46,647 --> 00:33:48,200
How come only the two of you came out?

406
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:50,046
Where are the other three?

407
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:18,240
Zhi Hua, you can't hold a grudge
like your Master Bai.

408
00:34:18,240 --> 00:34:22,160
How do you like the taste of your own poison?

409
00:34:22,160 --> 00:34:26,440
Though these people were greedy
and tried to learn every sect's skills,

410
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:28,240
that they fell into your trap.

411
00:34:28,240 --> 00:34:32,944
But there's no need for them
to die for pieces of trash like you.

412
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:37,450
Stop!

413
00:34:44,279 --> 00:34:45,799
It's about time.

414
00:34:45,799 --> 00:34:49,560
Zhi Hua. We'll settle our score here for today.

415
00:34:49,560 --> 00:34:53,347
But this isn't over between us.

416
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,879
This is My Lord's favorite tune.

417
00:35:27,879 --> 00:35:29,960
Since Yu Lian is no longer here,

418
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:32,947
I shall play it for him instead.

419
00:35:35,279 --> 00:35:38,222
Do you think I won't dare to kill you?

420
00:35:42,359 --> 00:35:44,279
Kill me?

421
00:35:44,279 --> 00:35:46,647
You wouldn't dare.

422
00:35:46,647 --> 00:35:49,913
Back then, you used others to kill
and wipe out my Bawang Manor.

423
00:35:49,913 --> 00:35:52,680
Then you hypocritically married me.

424
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:58,546
Wasn't it just to build a reputation
in the world for saving me from misery?

425
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:02,720
Furthermore, the birthday banquet is imminent.

426
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:04,400
If you kill me,

427
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:07,602
how will you explain it to the guests?

428
00:36:07,602 --> 00:36:10,520
Ever since your previous wife
was driven to her death by you,

429
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:13,359
there have been many rumors out there.

430
00:36:13,359 --> 00:36:17,080
Your long-planned great cause
is about to succeed.

431
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:20,422
Why would you risk any complications?

432
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:23,720
My Lady, you truly know me best.

433
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,720
After the birthday banquet,

434
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,959
you will take Yu Lian's place...

435
00:36:27,959 --> 00:36:31,400
and stay in this dark room forever,
playing music for me.

436
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:34,879
I want you to see with your own eyes
how those nobodies

437
00:36:34,879 --> 00:36:38,879
use Bawang Manor's Dragon Roar Swordplay
to kill people!

438
00:36:38,879 --> 00:36:40,971
Guards!

439
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:46,560
Any news on Zhi Hua?

440
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,439
Master, Zhi Hua went to Fenglai Pavilion.

441
00:36:48,439 --> 00:36:50,800
He hasn't returned yet.

442
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:52,200
Seal off the entire mansion immediately!

443
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:55,039
If Yu Lian escapes, everyone's head will roll!

444
00:36:55,039 --> 00:36:57,785
- Send men to keep a close watch on her.
- Yes, sir.

445
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:41,097
If you can't bring back Bai Yu Tang,

446
00:37:41,097 --> 00:37:44,117
I'll slaughter Chang Hong Bi tonight.

447
00:37:46,839 --> 00:37:49,947
Are you blind? Can't you see I'm right here?

448
00:37:53,319 --> 00:37:56,320
Master Zhi always talks big
in front of my father.

449
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,839
But when it comes to actually
getting things done,

450
00:37:58,839 --> 00:38:02,322
one might think you're in league with them.

451
00:38:03,839 --> 00:38:05,760
I've been working myself to the bone,

452
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:09,160
while you've done nothing but slack off.
And now you're here making sarcastic remarks.

453
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:11,160
You're just a bastard child.

454
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:14,267
How dare you put on airs before me,
the future sect master?

455
00:38:15,999 --> 00:38:17,271
I'll tell you the truth.

456
00:38:17,271 --> 00:38:19,160
Father told me everything.

457
00:38:19,160 --> 00:38:21,760
No matter how well you master
the Great Compassion Palm,

458
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:24,831
he will still have me inherit
the mantle of the Shangqing Sect.

459
00:38:25,399 --> 00:38:28,200
Now that you've caused such a disaster,

460
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:30,800
how can you have the nerve to compete with me?

461
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:33,447
You overconfident half-breed!

462
00:38:34,080 --> 00:38:37,983
You should take a good look at yourself.

463
00:38:39,479 --> 00:38:41,122
Zhi Hua.

464
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:16,240
How did it go? Did you succeed?

465
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:18,720
She's asking you. Did you succeed?

466
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:21,360
Zhao Hui has already taken her back.

467
00:39:23,879 --> 00:39:24,919
Don't worry.

468
00:39:24,919 --> 00:39:26,319
Your brother is fine.

469
00:39:26,319 --> 00:39:27,399
What?

470
00:39:27,399 --> 00:39:29,247
Brother?

471
00:39:33,479 --> 00:39:35,935
You still don't want to reunite?

472
00:39:48,919 --> 00:39:50,959
Yue Hua?

473
00:39:50,959 --> 00:39:52,560
Bai.

474
00:39:52,560 --> 00:39:55,439
Forgive me for hiding the truth.

475
00:39:55,439 --> 00:39:57,039
Zhan.

476
00:39:57,039 --> 00:40:01,640
The day we met, you were playing the tune
Father taught us as children.

477
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:03,822
I knew then that you recognized me.

478
00:40:03,822 --> 00:40:07,240
The reason I didn't acknowledge you
was because...

479
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:10,640
I didn't want to admit
that while you were seriously injured,

480
00:40:10,640 --> 00:40:12,600
I was the one who tried to kill you.

481
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:14,479
I understand.

482
00:40:14,479 --> 00:40:15,919
You had no choice.

483
00:40:15,919 --> 00:40:17,640
Look at me now.

484
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:19,359
Aren't I perfectly fine?

485
00:40:19,359 --> 00:40:20,633
Miss Yue Hua.

486
00:40:20,633 --> 00:40:22,412
You're truly remarkable now.

487
00:40:22,412 --> 00:40:25,160
When there's a chance,
I must have a proper spar with you.

488
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:28,435
To improve so much in just one year,

489
00:40:29,039 --> 00:40:31,240
you must have endured much hardship.

490
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:33,080
Your brother, Zhao Hui, is with us.

491
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,600
Do you want to go see him?

492
00:40:34,600 --> 00:40:36,080
Of course you do.

493
00:40:36,080 --> 00:40:39,359
- Zhao Hui would be so happy--
- No, I cannot see him.

494
00:40:39,359 --> 00:40:41,039
I hid in the Hanshui Palace.

495
00:40:41,039 --> 00:40:43,319
I even became a guard dog
at the Zhongxiao Pavilion,

496
00:40:43,319 --> 00:40:46,285
just for the chance to kill Jing Yi Ming.

497
00:40:46,285 --> 00:40:48,439
My task is not yet finished.

498
00:40:48,439 --> 00:40:49,800
I cannot give up halfway.

499
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,640
Yue Hua.

500
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:53,680
If you face Jing Yi Ming alone,

501
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:55,919
you have no chance of winning.

502
00:40:55,919 --> 00:40:57,439
The case he's involved in is massive.

503
00:40:57,439 --> 00:40:59,399
You are not the only one...

504
00:40:59,399 --> 00:41:02,200
whose blood is on his hands.

505
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,680
Leave him to me.

506
00:41:03,680 --> 00:41:04,760
No.

507
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:06,120
I swore an oath.

508
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:09,080
That I would kill Jing Yi Ming myself.

509
00:41:09,080 --> 00:41:11,280
Just pretend you never saw me.

510
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:13,122
Yue Hua!

511
00:41:13,122 --> 00:41:14,600
Let her go.

512
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:18,120
Even if she wants revenge,
she won't be reckless enough to go today.

513
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:20,310
We'll have another chance to persuade her.

514
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,959
Who did this?

515
00:41:44,959 --> 00:41:46,760
Bai Yu Tang.

516
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,439
You have so many men under you.

517
00:41:50,439 --> 00:41:55,200
How could he kill Xing Ze on my turf
and still manage to escape?

518
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:57,422
Please calm down, Master.

519
00:41:57,422 --> 00:41:59,160
When Bai Yu Tang...

520
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:00,640
came to cause trouble earlier,

521
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:02,839
I realized...

522
00:42:02,839 --> 00:42:05,319
he was using a feint to distract me,

523
00:42:05,319 --> 00:42:07,600
allowing Zhan Zhao to rescue.

524
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:09,839
I wanted to take men back to the manor
to provide reinforcements,

525
00:42:09,839 --> 00:42:11,560
but...

526
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:14,399
But Xing Ze refused to listen.

527
00:42:14,399 --> 00:42:18,254
He insisted on capturing Bai Yu Tang
as a birthday gift for you.

528
00:42:24,439 --> 00:42:27,110
Go and do two things immediately.

529
00:42:27,110 --> 00:42:28,680
First,

530
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:31,120
have Shao Ji Zu inform the county office.

531
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:34,439
Set up checkpoints at all four gates.
Do not let Zhan Zhao and the others escape!

532
00:42:34,439 --> 00:42:35,800
- Yes.
- At the same time,

533
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:38,999
have him lead a full search of Xiangyang
to find Yu Lian.

534
00:42:38,999 --> 00:42:41,539
He knows the gravity of this matter,
so he won't refuse.

535
00:42:41,539 --> 00:42:42,999
Second,

536
00:42:42,999 --> 00:42:46,039
All the girls and the death soldiers
at the Zhongxiao Pavilion...

537
00:42:46,039 --> 00:42:47,080
take a full tally!

538
00:42:47,080 --> 00:42:48,814
Yes, sir.
